    <item>
      <title>CAPS Context</title>
      <link>//localhost:3000/reference/caps-context/context/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>//localhost:3000/reference/caps-context/context/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;This page shows the source-documented &lt;code&gt;FsFlow.Caps.Context&lt;/code&gt; surface: the current-user model, request context record, request identifiers, locale, metadata, and request-scoped flags.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;context-types&#34;&gt;Context types&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;type &lt;a href=&#34;./usercontext.md&#34; class=&#34;broken-link&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;UserContext&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Represents the authenticated user attached to the current request. &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow.Caps.Context/Context.fs#L10&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;type &lt;a href=&#34;./requestcontext.md&#34; class=&#34;broken-link&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;RequestContext&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Represents the request-scoped execution context carried through FsFlow boundaries. &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow.Caps.Context/Context.fs#L29&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;current-user&#34;&gt;Current user&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;module &lt;code&gt;CurrentUser&lt;/code&gt;: Helpers for reading and shaping the current user context. &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow.Caps.Context/Context.fs#L56&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;./currentuser-create.md&#34; class=&#34;broken-link&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;CurrentUser.create&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Creates a current-user record from explicit values. &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow.Caps.Context/Context.fs#L81&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;./currentuser-fromclaimsprincipal.md&#34; class=&#34;broken-link&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;CurrentUser.fromClaimsPrincipal&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Creates a current-user record from a claims principal when the identity is authenticated. &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow.Caps.Context/Context.fs#L103&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;./currentuser-live.md&#34; class=&#34;broken-link&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;CurrentUser.live&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Reads the current claims principal from the runtime if one is available. &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow.Caps.Context/Context.fs#L136&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;./currentuser-hasrole.md&#34; class=&#34;broken-link&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;CurrentUser.hasRole&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Checks whether the current user has a role. &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow.Caps.Context/Context.fs#L146&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;./currentuser-claim.md&#34; class=&#34;broken-link&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;CurrentUser.claim&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Reads a claim value from the current user. &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow.Caps.Context/Context.fs#L156&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;request-context&#34;&gt;Request context&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;module &lt;code&gt;RequestContext&lt;/code&gt;: Helpers for building and reshaping request contexts. &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow.Caps.Context/Context.fs#L164&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;./requestcontext-create.md&#34; class=&#34;broken-link&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;RequestContext.create&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Creates a request context from explicit values. &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow.Caps.Context/Context.fs#L190&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;./requestcontext-live.md&#34; class=&#34;broken-link&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;RequestContext.live&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Creates a live request context from the current runtime state. &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow.Caps.Context/Context.fs#L215&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;./requestcontext-withrequestid.md&#34; class=&#34;broken-link&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;RequestContext.withRequestId&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Replaces the request identifier in a request context. &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow.Caps.Context/Context.fs#L231&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;./requestcontext-withcorrelationid.md&#34; class=&#34;broken-link&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;RequestContext.withCorrelationId&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Replaces the correlation identifier in a request context. &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow.Caps.Context/Context.fs#L240&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;./requestcontext-withtenantid.md&#34; class=&#34;broken-link&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;RequestContext.withTenantId&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Replaces the tenant identifier in a request context. &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow.Caps.Context/Context.fs#L249&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;./requestcontext-withcurrentuser.md&#34; class=&#34;broken-link&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;RequestContext.withCurrentUser&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Replaces the current user in a request context. &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow.Caps.Context/Context.fs#L258&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;./requestcontext-withculture.md&#34; class=&#34;broken-link&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;RequestContext.withCulture&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Replaces the culture in a request context. &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow.Caps.Context/Context.fs#L267&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;./requestcontext-withmetadata.md&#34; class=&#34;broken-link&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;RequestContext.withMetadata&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Replaces the request metadata in a request context. &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow.Caps.Context/Context.fs#L276&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;./requestcontext-withflags.md&#34; class=&#34;broken-link&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;RequestContext.withFlags&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Replaces the request-scoped flags in a request context. &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow.Caps.Context/Context.fs#L285&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;request-identity&#34;&gt;Request identity&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;module &lt;code&gt;RequestId&lt;/code&gt;: Helpers for the request identifier. &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow.Caps.Context/Context.fs#L291&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;./requestid-get.md&#34; class=&#34;broken-link&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;RequestId.get&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Reads the request identifier from a request context. &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow.Caps.Context/Context.fs#L298&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;./requestid-live.md&#34; class=&#34;broken-link&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;RequestId.live&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Returns a live request identifier from the current runtime state. &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow.Caps.Context/Context.fs#L306&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;module &lt;code&gt;CorrelationId&lt;/code&gt;: Helpers for the correlation identifier. &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow.Caps.Context/Context.fs#L311&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;./correlationid-tryget.md&#34; class=&#34;broken-link&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;CorrelationId.tryGet&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Reads the optional correlation identifier from a request context. &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow.Caps.Context/Context.fs#L318&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;./correlationid-live.md&#34; class=&#34;broken-link&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;CorrelationId.live&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Returns a live optional correlation identifier from the current runtime state. &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow.Caps.Context/Context.fs#L326&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;module &lt;code&gt;TenantId&lt;/code&gt;: Helpers for the tenant identifier. &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow.Caps.Context/Context.fs#L331&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;./tenantid-tryget.md&#34; class=&#34;broken-link&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;TenantId.tryGet&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Reads the optional tenant identifier from a request context. &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow.Caps.Context/Context.fs#L338&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;./tenantid-live.md&#34; class=&#34;broken-link&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;TenantId.live&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Returns a live optional tenant identifier from the current runtime state. &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow.Caps.Context/Context.fs#L346&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;module &lt;code&gt;Locale&lt;/code&gt;: Helpers for the current culture and locale. &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow.Caps.Context/Context.fs#L351&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;./locale-get.md&#34; class=&#34;broken-link&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;Locale.get&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Reads the culture from a request context. &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow.Caps.Context/Context.fs#L358&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;./locale-live.md&#34; class=&#34;broken-link&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;Locale.live&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Returns the current culture from the runtime state. &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow.Caps.Context/Context.fs#L366&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;metadata-and-flags&#34;&gt;Metadata and flags&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;module &lt;code&gt;RequestMetadata&lt;/code&gt;: Helpers for request metadata. &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow.Caps.Context/Context.fs#L371&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;./requestmetadata-empty.md&#34; class=&#34;broken-link&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;RequestMetadata.empty&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Creates an empty metadata map. &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow.Caps.Context/Context.fs#L378&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;./requestmetadata-frompairs.md&#34; class=&#34;broken-link&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;RequestMetadata.fromPairs&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Creates a metadata map from name/value pairs. &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow.Caps.Context/Context.fs#L386&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;./requestmetadata-tryget.md&#34; class=&#34;broken-link&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;RequestMetadata.tryGet&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Reads a metadata value by key if it exists. &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow.Caps.Context/Context.fs#L395&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;./requestmetadata-contains.md&#34; class=&#34;broken-link&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;RequestMetadata.contains&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Checks whether the metadata contains a key. &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow.Caps.Context/Context.fs#L404&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;module &lt;code&gt;RequestFlags&lt;/code&gt;: Helpers for request-scoped feature flags. &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow.Caps.Context/Context.fs#L410&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;./requestflags-empty.md&#34; class=&#34;broken-link&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;RequestFlags.empty&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Creates an empty flag map. &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow.Caps.Context/Context.fs#L417&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;./requestflags-frompairs.md&#34; class=&#34;broken-link&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;RequestFlags.fromPairs&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Creates a flag map from name/value pairs. &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow.Caps.Context/Context.fs#L425&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;./requestflags-tryget.md&#34; class=&#34;broken-link&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;RequestFlags.tryGet&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Reads a flag value by key if it exists. &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow.Caps.Context/Context.fs#L434&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;./requestflags-isenabled.md&#34; class=&#34;broken-link&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;RequestFlags.isEnabled&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Checks whether the supplied request-scoped flag is enabled. &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow.Caps.Context/Context.fs#L443&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;</description>
